  <description><![CDATA[<p>Lovingly run by the Wolf family, the small and attractive Haus Schrofenstein is beautifully furnished in traditional Austrian style. It offers great value and a good location just 5-10 minutes’ walk from the Oberlech lift and village centre. With an appealing Austrian interior encompassed with a cosy atmosphere, you’ll feel ‘at home’ and well cared for during your ski holiday in one of the world’s best known and exclusive ski resorts.</p>]]></description>
